<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Private Pottery Session Details</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Custom styles */
        .enroll-btn {
            background-color: #6d28d9;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .enroll-btn:hover {
            background-color: #4c1d95;
        }
        /* Style for the photo section */
        .photo-section {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
            gap: 10px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .photo-section img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .photo-section img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-800">
    <div class="container mx-auto py-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Private Pottery Session</h1>


        <div class="mb-8">
            <p class="mb-4">Immerse yourself in the artistry of pottery with our exclusive private sessions, meticulously crafted to provide a personalized and memorable experience. These one-hour clay sessions are designed for individuals who wish to spend an hour engaging in the creative process and leave with a beautiful, handcrafted pottery piece. Each session covers hand-built techniques, pinching, and personalization, ensuring that you not only enjoy the process but also create a unique clay masterpiece.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
            <p class="mb-4">Your journey begins with all materials and tools provided, eliminating the need for any additional expenses. The session fee of ₹1000 per person ensures an individualized experience, but for those looking to share the joy of pottery, we offer discounted rates of ₹900 each for groups of at least 4 participants and ₹800 each for larger groups of 9 or more.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
            <p class="mb-4">Sessions are available throughout the week, with three convenient time slots on weekdays (3 pm - 4 pm, 6 pm - 7 pm, and 7 pm - 8 pm, excluding Wednesdays) and flexible hours on Sundays from 11 am to 6 pm. To secure your preferred time, advance booking is essential, requiring a confirmation charge of ₹1000. Join us for an hour of creative expression, where you can delve into the world of pottery, craft something beautiful, and make your artistic vision come to life.</p>
        </div>

        
        <div class="photo-section">
            <img src="1.png" alt="Pottery Session" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg">
            <img src="Screenshot 2024-01-08 182800.png" alt="Pottery Session" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg">
            <img src="Screenshot 2024-01-08 185623.png" alt="Pottery Session" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg">
            <img src="Screenshot 2024-01-08 185710.png" alt="Pottery Session" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg">
            <img src="Screenshot 2024-01-08 185807.png" alt="Pottery Session" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg">
        </div>

        <!-- Enrollment section -->
        <div class="text-center my-12">
            <a href="/private" class="enroll-btn inline-block">Enroll Now</a>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 mt-8">Enroll in Private Pottery Session</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">Experience the joy of pottery in a personalized session.</p>
            <!-- Add enrollment form or additional details here -->
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
